en el lago Arenal disfrutando, de un hermoso paseo en Bote con la mejor vista del Volcán Arenal, conocerás la historia del Arenal y sus alrededores. Así como también disgustaras una rica copa de vino en medio de la Naturaleza \" text_color=\"#818181\" custom_icon_size=\"25\" text_left_padding=\"63\" icon_margin=\"3px 0 0 0 \"][vc_separator type=\"transparent\" position=\"center\" thickness=\"1\" up=\"20\" down=\"0\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row row_type=\"row\" type=\"full_width\" icon_pack=\"font_awesome\" content_menu_fe_icon=\"arrow_back\" text_align=\"left\"][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][call_to_action full_width=\"yes\" content_in_grid=\"yes\" type=\"normal\" fe_icon=\"arrow_back\" show_button=\"yes\" button_text=\"RESERVA YA\" background_color=\"#f5f5f5\" button_text_color=\"#ffffff\" button_hover_text_color=\"#ffffff\" button_background_color=\"#00ff00\" button_hover_background_color=\"#81d742\" button_border_color=\"#00ff00\" button_hover_border_color=\"#81d742\" box_padding=\"47px 0 47px 0\" button_link=\"http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/home-shop/\"]\r\n<h5>No se quede sin su inolvidable experiencia en Costa Rica, Venga y experiméntelo por usted mismo</h5>\r\n[/call_to_action][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][4k_icon icon_color=\"#3498db\" icon_size=\"50\" shape=\"none\" shape_type=\"solid\" border_radius=\"8\" shape_color=\"#dddddd\" shape_size=\"60\" hover_effect=\"none\" hover_on=\"icon\" float=\"none\" margin=\"20\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"1/1\"][4k_icon icon=\"ty2-sun\" icon_color=\"#939392\" icon_size=\"50\" shape=\"none\" shape_type=\"solid\" border_radius=\"8\" shape_color=\"#dddddd\" shape_size=\"60\" hover_effect=\"none\" hover_on=\"icon\" float=\"none\" margin=\"20\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home Default', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '19843-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-05-05 22:54:17', '2015-05-05 22:54:17', '', '19843', 'http://www.mmexperiencecr.com/2015/05/05/19843-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', ''